Portilla, a wonderful linguist,

00:05:26.140 --> 00:05:30.930
a really enormously important
historian, anthropologist,

00:05:30.930 --> 00:05:35.080
linguist who virtually single
handily rescued the language

00:05:35.080 --> 00:05:38.150
Nahuatl, which is the
language of the Maya

00:05:38.150 --> 00:05:39.970
