come to the theatre to see.

00:41:27.270 --> 00:41:30.990
And yet, preserving some of the
culture and some of the classics

00:41:30.990 --> 00:41:34.120
because we don't want
to forget [inaudible]

00:41:34.120 --> 00:41:36.900
and all the great Spanish
playwrights

00:41:36.900 --> 00:41:38.690
or Latino playwrights
